ance doesn't cover electrical problems.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/46.mp3","time_start":122.83,"time_end":125.91},{"position":47,"content":"It isn't an electrical problem.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/47.mp3","time_start":125.91,"time_end":127.55},{"position":48,"content":"The screen has a huge crack in it so it's unusable.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/48.mp3","time_start":127.55,"time_end":130.72},{"position":49,"content":"I see.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/49.mp3","time_start":130.72,"time_end":131.95},{"position":50,"content":"Any idea of the price to repair it?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/50.mp3","time_start":132.23,"time_end":134.56},{"position":51,"content":"No.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/51.mp3","time_start":134.56,"time_end":135.29},{"position":52,"content":"Well, I don't think it can be repaired.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/52.mp3","time_start":135.29,"time_end":137.59},{"position":53,"content":"It will need a new one.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/53.mp3","time_start":137.59,"time_end":139.19},{"position":54,"content":"Okay.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/54.mp3","time_start":139.19,"time_end":140.03},{"position":55,"content":"I'll make a note of that and we'll see what we can do.","a