t":"And how much do you think it will cost to replace it?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/64.mp3","time_start":163.0,"time_end":165.56},{"position":65,"content":"Well, when I bought it last year, I paid $125 for it.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/65.mp3","time_start":165.56,"time_end":171.09},{"position":66,"content":"But the one I've seen here in Sydney is a bit more expensive,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/66.mp3","time_start":171.09,"time_end":175.15},{"position":67,"content":"it's $140.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/67.mp3","time_start":175.15,"time_end":177.04},{"position":68,"content":"Right, and what was the third item?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/68.mp3","time_start":177.04,"time_end":179.36},{"position":69,"content":"My dining room table.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/69.mp3","time_start":179.64,"time_end":181.43},{"position":70,"content":"It's a lovely table from Indonesia.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/70.mp3","time_start":181.43,"time_end":183.92},{"position":71,"content":"It must have been very hot inside the container","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/71.mp3","time_start":183.92,"time_end":186.85},{"position":72,"content":"because one leg has completely split down the middle.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-2