th matching cups, saucers, the lot.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/81.mp3","time_start":217.68,"time_end":220.35},{"position":82,"content":"They were all in the one box which must have got dropped because some plates were broken - six actually.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/82.mp3","time_start":220.35,"time_end":227.13},{"position":83,"content":"And can you tell me the replacement value of these?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/83.mp3","time_start":227.13,"time_end":229.87},{"position":84,"content":"Well, it's hard to say because they were part of a set","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/84.mp3","time_start":229.87,"time_end":233.04},{"position":85,"content":"but they can be up to $10 each as it's such a good set.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/85.mp3","time_start":233.04,"time_end":236.72},{"position":86,"content":"Okay, so that would be around $60 altogether?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/86.mp3","time_start":236.72,"time_end":240.01},{"position":87,"content":"Yes, that's right.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/87.mp3","time_start":240.01,"time_end":241.4},{"position":88,"content":"And is that all of the items?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/88.mp3","time_start":241.4,"time_end":243.27},{"position":89,"content":"Yes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/89.mp3","time_start":243.27,"time_end":244.25},{"position":90,"content":"So what do I have to do now?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-2-part-1-2023-07-25-20-15-20/90.mp3","time_start":244.25,"time_end":246.63}]}